task.summary: Added a high-level expression for the ReLU layer
Added expressions for the first fully connected layer in a CNN
Type: added array constructor from the list of lengths. ONNX: added the Broadcastable trait for operators that support broadcasting and the Add operator.
Added MaxPool and Relu operators. Moved Broadcastable to the package object. Refactored Conv cosmetically.
Added the Reshape operator. Replaced all Ints with ArithExpr. Fixed a few typos.
Added the ONNX->MatMul operator. Fixed a few buygs in Reshape
Added an example of ONNX DSL operator composition. Fixed a few operator AST nodes-related bugs.
Fixed bugs in the tests and MaxPool operator.
